Trade/Device Name(s): Wondfo One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test Strip
Wondfo One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test Cassette
Wondfo One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test Midstream
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Wondfo One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test Strip, Cassette, and Midstream for qualitative detection of hCG in urine
Indications for Use Summary: A rapid chromatographic immunoassay for the qualitative detection of human chorionic gonadotropin (hCG) in urine, as an aid in early detection of pregnancy, in some cases as early as five days before the expected period.
